This Step is based on my setting in Terminal, I hope you know where you HOME DIRECTORY
Firstly you should download apache flume in the official website

or you can type brew install flume

nadess-MBP:~ leeheeyeon$ cd Downloads
nadess-MBP:Downloads leeheeyeon$ tar -xvzf apache-flume-1.7.0-bin.tar.gz

It will extract apache-flume-1.7.0-bin.tar.gz

and then 

nadess-MBP:Downloads leeheeyeon$ open -a Finder /usr/local/bin

your /usr/local/bin will open automatically, it will make easy to put 
